<small>Please help <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Ceteris_paribus&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Ceteris_paribus&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">to improve this article</a> to make it <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:NPOV" title="Wikipedia:NPOV" class="mw-redirect">neutral</a> in tone and meet Wikipedia's <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:STYLE" title="Wikipedia:STYLE" class="mw-redirect">quality standards</a>.</small></td>
